Dialogs.Dialog: Yeah. So, I need to get going.
I see. Sorry for stopping you.
No, don't worry. See you later.
(She's not as hard to approach as everyone says, eh...？)
Well, I guess I'll go home...
I was about to head home.
I see. Then how about we walk together？
(I just can't do it right. What should I do...？)
Hey, I have something I'd like you to teach me. Is that okay？
Eh？ You want me to？ ...Yes, if you think I can help.
Thank you. For example, when I do it like this...
That's it！ I understand it now.
I wonder if I was of any help.
(Everyone's still excited, even during a break.)
(Eh？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is spacing out alone again.)
For me... I guess it's the same as usual.
Ah, break time's over. See you later.
(It's time for a break. I'd better rest a bit.)
▲主人公＊▲. I'm going to the staff room for some class business.
I see, just as always. Anything I can help with？
Thanks. But I'm doing this because I like it.
Nah, just let me help. Come on.
Okay. Then I guess I'll ask for your help.
Actually, I have to be in the classroom before the bell rings.
Well, don't you need to be going？ I'm sorry that I talked so much. I should go now.
I'm so bored. Is there anything interesting...？
Ah！ Oh no. I shouldn't make Mama wait.
I see. You should go then.
Yeah, I'm sorry I took your time here. See you.
(It's rare for you to call out for me, huh ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Oh, I'm just picking up these balls during break time ▲主人公＊▲.
I see. Well, I'll help you then.
Thank you... Then please help me with this.
Oh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s rally is about to start.
You're in top condition, as usual right, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
▲主人公＊▲. Thank you. Um... did you notice anything wrong when you were watching me？ I mean, my form, perhaps...
You hit the balls too low！
I don't know. You and I are on different levels ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah, is that so？ Maybe you could tell me later if you notice something.
Ah, really？ Thank you. I'll pay more attention next time.
There's no problem at all. Don't worry too much！
I guess I'm on my prime condition today.
(Don't tell me she wasn't feeling very good about it...)
Ah, I don't understand what to do with this homework...
Ah, excuse me. I'm having a problem with the homework... I wonder if you can help me with it.
Ah, okay. Let's see if there's anything I can do.
You're right！ I understand now. You really saved me！
(You're getting easier to talk to lately ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Well, Suzuki-sensei asked me to do something, but I don't think I can do it alone...
Ah, then I'll help. What should we do？
Thank you very much！ I'm really sorry that you have to help me like this.
Don't mention it. I didn't have anything to do anyway. See you.
I'm here to buy something. How about you？
I came to buy something, too.
Ah, sorry. I've kept you occupied here.
No, it's fine. It turned out to be my lucky day today.
Um, I was just thinking of you. It was a surprise that you really appeared.
No, it's okay. I was the one who called out to you, and...
I thought that you looked familiar. Hehe, I'm glad that I chased after you.
Ah, sorry. I've kept you occupied here.
No. I really had fun, so it's okay. Bye.
So you have been watching ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yeah. You're working hard. How's everything？
Well then, how about we practice together？
Now I know how to move. You're really good at teaching the basics ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Hehe. No, you're really good at learning.
Yo, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Captain Tezuka is so cool, right？ I can't compare to him at all.
That's not the case. If you ask me, I would say that you are...
Sorry. My bad. Did you get hurt？
I'm okay. It didn't hit me. It just surprised me.
Ah, such a cruel comment. Hehe.
(You have become more cheerful lately, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Eh？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you need anything？
No, I'm just wondering how you're doing.
I have to go. Somehow, I've become quite talkative lately.
Why are you here？ Ah, is it possible that you came to see me？
Yeah. I kind of wanted to talk with you.
Then, why didn't you come inside？
I had fun. Can I come here again？
I have to say sorry too. Hehe, now I'm here.
Did you just run along the corridor？
A little bit. Our break time is too short.
Ah, I'll have to go. Don't run down the corridor, okay？
(You have become more cheerful lately, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Come on. No one's watching now... Okay？
Come on. No one's watching now... Okay？
H-Here...？ But... people will probably come...
I didn't say no... You're so naughty...
Come on. No one's watching now... Okay？
What...？ You shouldn't... Not in a place like this.
Okay, that's it. Someone might see us...
Hmm... Somehow it's just the two of us now...
Hmm... Somehow it's just the two of us now...
Then... Just a little bit, okay？
Hmm... Somehow it's just the two of us now...
Hey... You're so selfish！ How about doing it before someone comes？
Hey, don't get too carried away！
See？ No one is watching, right？
Here, at school...？ We shouldn't do this.
See？ No one is watching us.
Here... You know we're at school, right？
Then we do it as students.
See？ No one is watching us.
Don't tell me... You want to do it here？
This is not good. What if someone sees us...？
Hey！ Doing this at school？ Reflect on your actions！
